posts.post_title: SOLD - lot of 21 raw T206 - Piedmont 150 and 350-460
posts.post_content:
Up for sale is a lot of 21 T206 Piedmont commons.  There are two duplicates (Criss and Williams).  All are in PR to Good+ shape, with the exception of the two horizontal cards, which have both (obviously) been trimmed.

Looking for $SOLD for the lot, which works out to about $XX.XX a card + a little for shipping.  I would prefer to not break up the lot, so please don't ask unless you are making a strong offer on a specific card.

All will be shipped in top loaders (w/ penny sleeves).  First to PM or email me at [url]h2oya311@yahoo.com[/url] will be the new owner.

See scans below for condition or ask me if you need any details.
